line_1: And lessening orbs on lessening orbs encroach; —
line_2: Near and more near your beamy cars approach,

line_1: "With humble bows; nor white-glov'd beaus encroach
line_2: "In crowds behind, to guard me to my coach.

line_1: Yet on her Beauties durst not Art incroach;
line_2: As nearer to his Farm you made Approach,
